Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.69,0:01:05.99,EN-op,,0,0,0,,I've been wandering around
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.99,0:01:10.39,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I've been deceived everything. At that time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.75,0:01:15.44,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Then you appeared in front of me. You ignited my pale heart
