Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.02,0:01:31.92,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}朦朧とした理想を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.69,0:01:35.67,JP-op,,0,0,0,,もう無駄にしないようにと
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.67,0:01:40.29,JP-op,,0,0,0,,悲しみを切り刻んだ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.31,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.31,0:01:46.54,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.56,0:01:50.73,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Just now. Chip at your heart. We just fight for freedom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.86,0:01:55.44,JP-op,,0,0,0,,奪い合って　汚し合って
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.44,0:01:59.63,JP-op,,0,0,0,,それでも守りたくて
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.03,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.03,0:02:05.49,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.50,0:02:10.00,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}We don't want to go through that again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.00,0:02:15.57,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}時は満ちた　始まりの鐘が鳴る
